                    House, Progressive House | On Air Records

            320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-09-13 | 03:44:38 | 518 Mb


We didn't want to release a classical ibiza closing compilation! We don't want the summer to end! Never ending summer in Miami, Frankfurt, Amsterdam, Rimini, St. Tropez, Istanbul, Mykonos and where ever Never Ending Summer in... Ibiza! (Presented By A.C.K.) Incl. different kind of house styles and many Balearic and latin flavoured tracks and remixes from some HQ house producer and DJ's like My Digital Enemy, Dave Kurtis, Luna Moor, Coqui Selection, Nick & Danny Chatelain, Ivan Pica, The Henchmen & Nemanja Stamenkovic, Damir Pushkar, A.C.K., John De Mark, John PC, Subcquence & Aad Mouthaan, Souljackerz, Michael Paterson & Warner Powers, Sanya Shelest & DJ Flight, Pagano, Reza, The Glitterboys, Lissat & Voltaxx, Rio Dela Duna, Lexvaz & JJ Mullor, Chris Montana & Chris Bekker, Peter Brown, Voltereto, Phil Weeks, Serin Control, Michael Salamon, Alfred Azzetto, Valentino Sky, Alban Berisha, Fra'n'Kie, David Herrero, Sola & Diaz, Sean Finn, Marcos Cruz, Filippo Fedetto, Alex Roque, Daviddance, Dino Mileta,Cole Jonson, Michael Fall - Perfumed Garden, DJ Groove Colombia & Florian Gasperini, DJane Thunderpussy, Alex Faraci, Massimo Russo, Joshua (Italy), Pablo Santana, Sebastian Moreno, DJ Evgrand and more!
